<title>USA: American Eco to acquire Doug Chalmers.</title>
<headline>American Eco to acquire Doug Chalmers.</headline>
<dateline>HOUSTON 1996-08-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>American Eco Corp said on Friday that it has signed a Letter of Intent to acquire all of the shares of Doug Chalmers Construction Ltd of Sarnia, Ontario, Canada.</p>
<p>Chalmers is a scaffolding, industrial, and civil engineering construction company serving the refinery and petrochemical industries in the Ontario refinery belt.</p>
<p>The offer will be conditional upon requisite regulatory approval and after American Eco has satisfactorily completed its due diligence for Board approval.</p>
